Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.91,0:00:03.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为果然还是被骂了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.16,0:00:06.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像要吃了我似的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.58,0:00:08.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是我说「要离家出走」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.46,0:00:10.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她就说「有本事就走啊」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.42,0:00:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正你一句我一句的…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.15,0:00:14.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿海？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.88,0:00:16.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你…这玩意…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.01,0:00:18.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有这个我睡不着
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.04,0:00:19.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这毛巾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.87,0:00:22.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有这个我也睡不着
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.75,0:00:24.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是有多想睡好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.27,0:00:26.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静下来好好想想
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.23,0:00:28.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离家出走也顶不过几天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.17,0:00:32.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学校也不能不去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.82,0:00:34.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好意思说这话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.37,0:00:35.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听我说 安城
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.76,0:00:40.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学校啊 只要一回不去 以后会很麻烦的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.23,0:00:42.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起初倒是挺轻松
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.31,0:00:45.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算一整天不去 也不会有任何变化
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.28,0:00:50.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是啊 因为不会变就日复一日地攒下去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.83,0:00:52.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回过神来自己已经彻底…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.15,0:00:57.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 这种事还真轮不到我教育别人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.27,0:00:57.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.52,0:01:01.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊 说得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.24,0:01:05.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿海真厉害 家里蹲不是白蹲的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.52,0:01:06.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.63,0:01:08.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然 宿海还是宿海
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.63,0:01:12.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己够呛的时候 还总想着别人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.95,0:01:17.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我适可而止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.77,0:01:21.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你总是这样在意别人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.32,0:01:27.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不是那样 面麻比我更…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.54,0:01:33.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那啥…我和雪集也谈过了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.64,0:01:37.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们一直是活在面麻的阴影中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.77,0:01:39.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样不太好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.55,0:01:42.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可面麻现在就在我家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.34,0:01:44.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 所以…那种事…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.80,0:01:48.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不相信面麻的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.83,0:01:51.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有 不是不信
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.50,0:01:55.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我差不多该回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.76,0:01:57.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等啊 宿海
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.68,0:02:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我给你买了牛肉咖喱哦 安鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.35,0:02:14.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,520日元哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.92,0:02:20.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牛肉咖喱撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.09,0:02:24.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是误会 我只是来看日记…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.46,0:02:29.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的牛肉咖喱！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.87,0:04:10.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看完这个 也许就能知道面麻的愿望了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.37,0:04:12.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.98,0:04:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所不了解的面麻 就在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.30,0:04:21.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所不知道的面麻的内心 就在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.12,0:04:27.50,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天和大家一起玩了 好好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.26,0:04:36.12,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天和大家一起玩了 好开心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.74,0:04:37.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.53,0:04:38.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好随意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.36,0:04:41.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是好玩就是开心 只有这点差别
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.34,0:04:45.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她本来就不擅长作文
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.37,0:04:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里有点不一样耶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.90,0:04:51.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天和大家一起玩的时候摔了一跤 好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.45,0:04:53.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 这里也不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.19,0:04:57.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天大家一起去探望仁碳的妈妈了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.23,0:05:01.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,探病啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.40,0:05:04.40,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,病房入口 门诊入口
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.26,0:05:06.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来 我们经常一大堆人去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.64,0:05:09.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.79,0:05:14.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳的妈妈 一直都在住院呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.11,0:05:17.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啦 给神写封信吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.12,0:05:21.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,写「请让仁碳的妈妈快些好起来」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.00,0:05:22.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么弄
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.75,0:05:27.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳 看那个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.23,0:05:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 是那时候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.18,0:05:41.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.26,0:05:47.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家决定一起制作烟花 我感觉好难
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.02,0:05:50.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 我会加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.27,0:05:56.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想起来了 说是把信装进火箭烟花寄给神
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.63,0:05:59.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 愿望会不会就是这个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.63,0:06:04.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊 一定是 那时候想做但没成功啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.67,0:06:05.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 宿海
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.81,0:06:09.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了我妈妈…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.06,0:06:18.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢吞仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.95,0:06:20.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不良仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.08,0:06:22.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坏蛋仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.33,0:06:27.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.50,0:06:42.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁要理什么仁碳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.17,0:06:54.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大半夜吃东西 会变猪的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.80,0:06:56.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要变猪的是你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.97,0:07:03.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盐拉面 加了蛋花汤的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.67,0:07:06.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为没有小健拉面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.31,0:07:10.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是想喂你点东西吃 哄你开心一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.88,0:07:12.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.50,0:07:18.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.84,0:07:21.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸差不多快回来了 快点吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.04,0:07:26.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 明天我也会去上学
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.23,0:07:30.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 你别跟过来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.06,0:07:35.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盯…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.50,0:07:38.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.96,0:07:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你奖励 张嘴…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.32,0:07:44.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.26,0:07:49.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 不能再做些奇怪的事情了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.73,0:07:56.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是 为什么不去上学又穿着校服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.49,0:08:00.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么嘛 穿什么都是自由打扮…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.36,0:08:01.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.95,0:08:06.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据火药类管制法规定 使用烟花的火药
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.66,0:08:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须年满18周岁 拥有国家资格
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.01,0:08:11.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.90,0:08:14.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩具烟花一类的话 倒是勉强可以
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.39,0:08:16.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过也需要许可证的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.46,0:08:20.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 果然不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.50,0:08:24.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊 正常想想烟花的确需要资格…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.82,0:08:27.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说 昨天扫除的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.93,0:08:31.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是认真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.05,0:08:37.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收集大量烟花 把火药分别弄出集中到一起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.98,0:08:41.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞进厕纸芯里面 但是会烧起来所以不行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.13,0:08:42.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不明摆着的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.76,0:08:44.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怖 小鬼好恐怖
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.92,0:08:49.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 以前我们却认为这个可行的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.94,0:08:55.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前弄成这样 也真的以为它能飞起来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.67,0:09:02.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以为能做得比祭典上看到的更大 飞得更高
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.38,0:09:11.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞起来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.07,0:09:13.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时还觉得高中生完全是大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.01,0:09:18.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了那年纪什么都能做得到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.19,0:09:30.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉反而是那时候 我们什么都做得到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.36,0:09:36.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之先想想办法 找找大体的方向
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.91,0:09:39.07,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「停」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.97,0:09:42.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话虽如此 可不管怎么想 这也没戏的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.46,0:09:43.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.24,0:09:48.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做这么多事 可如果不是你所说的面麻的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.53,0:09:49.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是无用功
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.04,0:09:55.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 宿海君 你有好好向你那的面麻确认过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.04,0:09:56.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.56,0:10:01.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向本人…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.68,0:10:06.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向她本人确认 我可能是有些害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.92,0:10:09.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.46,0:10:12.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才一瞬间似曾相识
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.75,0:10:15.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是先人一步的宿海
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.37,0:10:18.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和只能可怜巴巴望着他的雪集君
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.24,0:10:23.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 为什么没说出来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.16,0:10:29.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天也是 要不是他召集大家去秘密基地的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.00,0:10:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天 不是面麻提议的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.24,0:10:38.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 对 我被面麻一个电话叫了出去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.19,0:10:39.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电话？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.18,0:10:45.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 对 那天她好像有什么事要商量
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.92,0:10:48.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易回想起来的 为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.39,0:10:50.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为宿海在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.68,0:10:53.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你忘记了一件重要的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.91,0:11:00.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻说过「集会的事情 不要告诉宿海」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.45,0:11:04.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻说的？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.84,0:11:06.08,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第7话 真正的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.07,0:11:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烟花？我认识会做的人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.58,0:11:11.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.33,0:11:13.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们工地的一个大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.86,0:11:16.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是祭典的时候会兼做烟花师
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.19,0:11:19.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么 仁太 想做烟花吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.29,0:11:21.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 啊 嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.69,0:11:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.73,0:11:25.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问我为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.71,0:11:26.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是想做来的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.99,0:11:27.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.98,0:11:30.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 还有波波他们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.94,0:11:35.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.82,0:11:37.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.82,0:11:40.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊 那我去拜托他一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.59,0:11:44.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳仁碳仁碳仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.80,0:11:47.75,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走不出空达尔城啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.04,0:11:47.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要吗 我先帮你联络一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.91,0:11:49.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这事下次再说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.91,0:11:56.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 简单的也要花这么多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.47,0:11:59.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒也不是不能给你做
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.92,0:12:09.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来 怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.49,0:12:14.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,20万？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.69,0:12:17.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 这么多钱见都没见过啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.33,0:12:19.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.03,0:12:23.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 总有办法的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.58,0:12:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我和安鸣去拼命打工 对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.50,0:12:29.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下 别擅自决定好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.85,0:12:30.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打工
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.04,0:12:32.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么不好嘛 这叫相互帮助吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.98,0:12:33.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.87,0:12:36.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,担心啥 安鸣一周打七天工的话轻松搞定
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.84,0:12:39.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么啊 我还没说要干呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.38,0:12:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算我一个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.54,0:12:42.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要…打工
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.46,0:12:47.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里输入金额知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.13,0:12:50.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是半旧货的价格 这边是新商品的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.93,0:12:53.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 然后在这里输入差额吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.90,0:12:58.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我花了1个月才掌握的技巧 你一上手就…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.99,0:13:00.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…这花的时间也太久了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.34,0:13:04.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.51,0:13:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.14,0:13:09.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这方面却完全不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.55,0:13:11.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啰嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.44,0:13:13.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦 又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.80,0:13:14.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.89,0:13:16.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 果然是那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.69,0:13:17.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传闻的那个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.84,0:13:19.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打工倒是有来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.68,0:13:21.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学校那边就请假
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.93,0:13:24.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 那不是不来上学的家伙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.51,0:13:25.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.57,0:13:26.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么 他们俩搞上了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.77,0:13:28.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好 我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.29,0:13:31.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢~迎~光~临！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.59,0:13:38.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.47,0:13:41.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.21,0:13:46.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.10,0:13:50.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.11,0:13:54.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉现在这个样子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.09,0:13:57.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就和小时候一样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.96,0:14:01.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳 给我胶布
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.69,0:14:09.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿…海…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.48,0:14:13.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给 安鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.10,0:14:16.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准这么叫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.34,0:14:17.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接得漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.02,0:14:25.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿海在打工啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.85,0:14:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烟花的事 他好像是认真的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.78,0:14:33.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备怎么办 我们也来凑凑钱？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.17,0:14:36.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去陪宿海疯吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.00,0:14:38.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不参加的话我也就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.34,0:14:42.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 要不要出来一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.15,0:14:45.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去喝杯茶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.84,0:14:49.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上考试了 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.75,0:14:51.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是年级第四
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.42,0:14:54.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年级第二的某人在说什么呢 再见
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.90,0:15:02.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟紧你的脚步 可是相当费力的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.86,0:15:08.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.37,0:15:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.58,0:15:15.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳 居然这么晚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.62,0:15:16.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不良！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.81,0:15:19.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.03,0:15:21.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去洗个澡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.95,0:15:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳 绝对有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.86,0:15:30.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上倒头就睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.20,0:15:32.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.84,0:15:34.29,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.15,0:15:34.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清早飞快就出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.50,0:15:37.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是今日小狗专栏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.79,0:15:41.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果小狗狗是母的 我就认定仁碳在做什么奇怪的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.42,0:15:46.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的小狗 奥斯卡尔酱 母 7岁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.95,0:15:49.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴哥犬好可爱 这褶皱也好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.31,0:15:50.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是母的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.24,0:15:55.39,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…向小客人们打招呼说欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.10,0:15:59.87,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托奥斯卡尔酱的福 客人增多了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.69,0:15:53.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.92,0:15:57.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.93,0:16:00.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 那请在这名册上签个字
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.86,0:16:02.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好的 嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.75,0:16:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说 仁太君退学了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.99,0:16:09.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有啊…不过 为什么这么问呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.09,0:16:12.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起啊 问这种奇怪的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.91,0:16:15.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 我最近看见他好像在打工
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.82,0:16:22.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在想仁太君有没有把这些都告诉你啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.51,0:16:27.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有 不过我们家是自由主义
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.78,0:16:31.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都由他自己去决定的 没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.74,0:16:32.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有事！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.03,0:16:38.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有事有事有事 有事！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.57,0:16:45.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.29,0:16:55.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波波？嗯 我没班 店长好像挺中意他
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.72,0:16:58.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上他是和你一起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.34,0:17:01.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 羊山的施工地？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.95,0:17:03.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一来就干那个也太累了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.73,0:17:08.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是没错啦 赚钱的话还是体力活最快
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.54,0:17:12.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火箭式烟花什么的 花钱如流水啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.35,0:17:16.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烟花
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.81,0:17:22.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愿望…面麻的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.53,0:17:25.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多为自己想想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.62,0:17:28.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这态度 让人烦躁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.72,0:17:37.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 也是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.59,0:17:41.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说 雪集和鹤子那边有联络过你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.60,0:17:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 倒是经常有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.64,0:17:45.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们要是也来多好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.14,0:17:47.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明挺担心仁碳的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.85,0:17:49.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.11,0:17:53.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 仁碳就是仁碳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.47,0:17:56.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不也这么叫吗 我叫他仁碳哪里不对啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.30,0:17:58.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.43,0:18:02.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.31,0:18:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新来的 这边
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.15,0:18:11.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.26,0:18:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后来这边
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.24,0:18:17.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.96,0:18:20.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙 挺卖力的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.42,0:18:27.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 仁碳可帅了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.69,0:18:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在面麻没有为自己想的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.51,0:18:45.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳却一直在想着面麻的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.85,0:18:49.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心脚下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.95,0:18:50.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.21,0:19:07.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 什么情况
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.12,0:19:10.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别随便动灯照的方向啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.96,0:19:11.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.03,0:19:13.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是风…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.16,0:19:16.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风能移动照明灯吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.80,0:19:26.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帅极了 闪闪发光的仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.48,0:19:33.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帅极了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.59,0:19:42.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.14,0:19:45.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做了好多好多
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.35,0:19:46.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再多也得有个限度吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.19,0:19:55.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.11,0:19:56.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.51,0:20:00.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我妈做的味道好接近
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.34,0:20:06.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 仁碳 在学校辛苦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.60,0:20:10.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过好像也挺开心的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.09,0:20:12.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开心？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.62,0:20:17.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我感觉啊 意外地比总是宅在家里要轻松
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.91,0:20:20.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有种活着的实感吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.03,0:20:22.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活着
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.32,0:20:26.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 不是说实际上怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.93,0:20:29.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是说一直以来我都太…那什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.87,0:20:30.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻也觉得…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.69,0:20:37.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看着感觉自己活着的仁碳 面麻也觉得自己活着的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.28,0:20:38.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.29,0:20:46.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 我们先把定金带来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.69,0:20:50.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然还远远不够
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.42,0:20:53.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有这些 能不能先开始制作呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.18,0:20:54.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.21,0:21:00.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个啊 不好意思 这事吹了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.68,0:21:04.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不小心跟祭典的负责人说了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.94,0:21:08.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被他骂说「居然帮高中生做这种事」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.20,0:21:10.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.68,0:21:11.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么能…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.57,0:21:12.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们这么拼命耶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.87,0:21:15.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说的负责人是哪位
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.68,0:21:17.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我直接和他谈谈去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.62,0:21:20.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是本间家的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.19,0:21:25.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻家的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.26,0:21:37.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 仁太君他们在为你做各种努力哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.91,0:21:44.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是乱来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.60,0:22:59.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐我啊 可是超和平Busters的
